{"task_id": "SPEC-001", "timestamp": "2026-01-06T15:40:11Z", "category": "data", "component_name": "Card", "description": "Content container for entry-level information in dashboards, galleries, catalogs. Contains CardTitle, CardBody, CardFooter. Variant='secondary' for secondary styling. Supports expandable cards with CardExpandableContent. Can be used as selectable tiles (tile component deprecated).", "usage_example": "<Card><CardTitle>Task Details</CardTitle><CardBody>Description here</CardBody><CardFooter>Actions</CardFooter></Card>", "source_url": "https://www.patternfly.org/components/card/"}
